Package: ggrose
Title: Plot Nightingale Rose Map
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
    person("Jing","Zhang",role = c("aut", "cre"),email = "zj391120@163.com"),
    person("Zhi", "Jin", role="aut")
    )
Description: Nightingale rose map is useful for display data. Traditional method using
    pacakge 'ggplt2' is depend on coord_polar() function to curve the axis from bar plot.
    This package provides a new layer and methord, by split a whole circle, to create this map directly and easily.
